  "ko_l1_culture_001_conveniencestore_001": "韓國的便利商店很方便。",
  "ko_l1_culture_001_conveniencestore_002": "全天營業。",
  "ko_l1_culture_001_conveniencestore_003": "肚子餓的時候隨時都可以去。",
  "ko_l1_culture_001_conveniencestore_004": "很多人吃拉麵。",
  "ko_l1_culture_001_conveniencestore_005": "杯麵種類非常多。",
  "ko_l1_culture_001_conveniencestore_006": "這裡有熱水和微波爐。",
