  "ko_l1_culture_003_seasons_012": "吃清涼的西瓜。",
  "ko_l1_culture_003_seasons_013": "秋天很涼爽。",
  "ko_l1_culture_003_seasons_014": "樹葉變紅又變黃。",
  "ko_l1_culture_003_seasons_015": "天空晴朗高遠。",
  "ko_l1_culture_003_seasons_016": "去賞楓。",
